    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Well it's working to the extent of the behavior of the component when unmounting. The state is stored in the store and thus it is decoralated from the component state. On the other hand if the component implement a clean up on unmounting then it will be cleared. And it would make sense to clean up because there is no mean to opt out part of the store. Also, applying some ui filters that were hidden by a user action is not a straightforward behavior. I mean you hide something and yet it stills applies is confusing, right?\n",
